<form action="search.php" method="get">
  <input type="text" name="query" />
  <input type="submit" value="Search" />
</form>

Sanitize and escape user inputs – Use libraries like OWASP's ESAPI for encoding.
Content Security Policy (CSP) – Use CSP headers to limit what JavaScript is executed.
Use frameworks with built-in protections – Many modern frameworks include automatic escaping of user inputs.
